CodeSystem: Norwegian Laboratory Codebook

Official URL: http://hl7.no/fhir/ig/nlk-test/CodeSystem/norsk-laboratoriekodeverk Version: 0.1.0
Active as of 2025-09-24 Computable Name: NorskLaboratoriekodeverk

Norwegian Laboratory Codebook - a comprehensive terminology for laboratory medicine in Norway

This Code system is referenced in the content logical definition of the following value sets:

  • This CodeSystem is not used here; it may be used elsewhere (e.g. specifications and/or implementations that use this content)

Properties

This code system defines the following properties for its concepts

NameCodeTypeDescription
validFrom validFrom dateTime Valid from date
validTo validTo dateTime Valid to date
replacedBy replacedBy code Code that replaces this code
changeDate changeDate dateTime Date of last change
codeDefinition codeDefinition string Technical code definition
component component string Component being measured
componentSpec componentSpec string Component specification
system system string System/specimen type
systemSpec systemSpec string System specification
propertyType propertyType string Type of property measured
propertySpec propertySpec string Property specification
unit unit string Unit of measurement
primaryDomain primaryDomain string Primary medical domain
secondaryDomain secondaryDomain string Secondary medical domain
grouping grouping string Grouping category
